data.description: Beautiful Ranch home with full basement on private cul-de-sac lot. Lots of updates and features inside this spacious home! New windows on the main floor, HVAC & water heater replaced in 2021. Walking inside the front door your immediately greeted in the den with a cozy wood burning fireplace and built in shelving. Huge living room with ample seating space perfect for entertaining. Nicely appointed kitchen with upgraded counter tops, tile back splash, and coffee bar. Large formal dining room with built in storage cabinets. Spacious primary bedroom suite with walk in closet. Three additional bedrooms all feature original hardwood floors and lots of natural light. The basement of this home offers endless opportunity’s from home gym, play room, office, theater, flex space or all of the above. Lower level also has full bath and kitchen space. The large deck overlooking the back of the property is perfect for your next summer BBQ. (Deck is not permitted.)
